253
00:16:52,595 --> 00:16:54,175
Oh.

254
00:16:54,175 --> 00:16:57,655
Speaking of which, why not sell aunt's clothes at the bazaar?

255
00:16:57,655 --> 00:17:00,995
Good idea! It's better than throwing them away.

256
00:17:00,995 --> 00:17:03,058
I'm sure mom would be happy about that too.

257
00:17:03,058 --> 00:17:06,698
Sustainable, right?

