274
00:18:38,919 --> 00:18:42,425
Uncle, where are aunt's clothes? I'm bringing them over.

275
00:18:42,425 --> 00:18:45,505
Oh, right. Thanks. They're in a box in the closet.

276
00:18:45,505 --> 00:18:47,045
Got it.

277
00:19:07,412 --> 00:19:09,990
Ah, you definitely look better like that.

278
00:19:09,990 --> 00:19:12,954
Okay, once you're done with the marriage meeting, be sure to turn up.

279
00:19:12,954 --> 00:19:13,965
Sure.

280
00:19:13,965 --> 00:19:17,130
- I'm ready.
- All right.

281
00:19:17,695 --> 00:19:19,305
Let's go.

282
00:19:19,305 --> 00:19:21,355
Later.

283
00:19:22,665 --> 00:19:26,975
- Hayate, that looks heavy.
- I'm fine.

284
00:19:29,852 --> 00:19:32,122
Wait for me!

285
00:19:33,562 --> 00:19:36,532
- Here you go.
- Okay, got it.

286
00:19:37,911 --> 00:19:40,321
- Thank you!
- Thank you very much!

287
00:19:40,321 --> 00:19:42,811
Hello. Welcome!

288
00:19:49,122 --> 00:19:50,772
Hayate.

289
00:19:50,772 --> 00:19:53,030
- You're Hayate-kun, right?
- Yes, hello.

290
00:19:53,030 --> 00:19:54,922
I miss you!

291
00:19:54,922 --> 00:19:57,730
- I've been wanting to meet you!
- Huh? Why?

292
00:19:57,730 --> 00:19:59,698
If I want to see you,

293
00:19:59,698 --> 00:20:04,090
