298
00:20:16,048 --> 00:20:18,762
- Let's go!
- But Kyoka! Wait!

299
00:20:18,762 --> 00:20:19,858
See you.

300
00:20:19,858 --> 00:20:23,532
Kyoka-chan! Wait a minー! Kyoka-chan!

301
00:20:23,532 --> 00:20:26,192
