479
00:31:19,025 --> 00:31:23,795
She has a bob hairstyle and wears yellow clothes. Could we take a look inside...?

480
00:31:23,795 --> 00:31:25,835
Bob hairstyle and yellow clothes.

481
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:30,635
