00:31:47,675 --> 00:31:50,158
Super cute...

491
00:31:50,158 --> 00:31:53,158
<i>Super cute...</i>

492
00:32:11,650 --> 00:32:13,525
P-Please put on your glasses.

493
00:32:13,525 --> 00:32:15,745
- Your glasses.
- Glasses?

494
00:32:15,745 --> 00:32:19,451
<i>Glasses, glasses...</i>

